HEADWORD: Rimau dahan
<hw>Ri"mau da"han</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From the native Oriental
name.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The clouded tiger cat (<spn>Felis
marmorata</spn>) of Southern Asia and the East Indies.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

